Rashard Mendenhall scored on an 8-
yard touchdown run for the Pittsburgh Steelers, who trail the
Green Bay Packers 21-17 during the third quarter of the Super
Bowl at  Cowboys Stadium  in Arlington,  Texas .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
